ComicInfo.Title: Part 3 of 5: Tiffany Blues
ComicInfo.Summary: The Toymaker saves Tiffany from the clutches of the Baron, and the pair escape the city to start a new life in Paris. There an old scientist, Giraud, offers the hope that the pair can have their dreams fulfilled. But for their dreams to become reality, a nightmare must be faced.
